<title>USA: Network Computing to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>Network Computing to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 1997-04-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Network Computing Devices Inc said the board of directors has adopted a program to repurchase up to one million shares of common stock during the 12-month period ending April 30, 1998.</p>
<p>The company said that the purchases will be made on the open market using the company's own cash resources. The shares repurchased will be used to fund the company's stock compensation plans and other corporate purchases.</p>
